high_descs: Turn around and walk to the dining table.
Pick up the mug from the dining table.
Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Heat up the mug in the microwave.
Move away slightly back from the counter top.
Open the bottom right cabinet and put the mug in it.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated mug in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around to your left and walk towards the table
Pick up the cup on the edge of the table
Turn to your left and walk towards the microwave
Open the microwave and put the cup inside beside the two apple then close the microwave; open it again pick up the cup
Turn around and face the cabinet under the microwave
Open the cabinet and put the cup inside the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put the cup from the microwave to the cabinet

high_descs: Turn around towards the circle table.
Pick up the coffee cup in front of the bread on the table.
Turn around and walk towards the microwave.
Place the cup inside the microwave, heat it up, and take it back out.
Take a step backwards to look at the right cabinet beneath the microwave.
Place the cup in the cabinet and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed cup from the table into the cabinet beneath the microwave.
